    <string name="about_app">Note</string>
    <string name="must_read">This APP supports running stable diffusion image generation on CPU/GPU and some Qualcomm NPUs.\n\nSD1.5 models are supported on Snapdragon NPUs with Hexagon V68 architecture or newer.\n\nSDXL models are supported on Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 and newer devices.\n\nIf your chip is outside the above scope, you can only run on CPU/GPU.\n\nThis project is a fork of https://github.com/xororz/local-dream\n\nThis software is provided for learning purposes only. If you encounter any issues, please resolve them yourself. No technical support or service is provided.\n\nTHE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED \"AS IS\", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. USE AT YOUR OWN RISK.</string>
